snippet.title: The Archives - Gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
Find out what is included in The Archives of Evil Dr BA, now on Itch.io


3 Java games, old and less old, for hours of fun, and with full sources! Play them, change them, share them. You are even allowed to sell your new games!


Discover on Itch.io: https://abecam.itch.io/the-archives-of-evil-dr-ba
